               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of John the Baptist, መልክአ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ፡, God Reigns, እግዚአብሔር፡ ነግሠ፡ (ነግሥ፡), Image of Gäbrä Mänfas Qǝddus, መልክአ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡, Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡, Image of Gabriel, መልክአ ገብርኤል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="10v" facs="003">Fols 1r–10v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2999RepCh279">Hymn to John the
                                                  Baptist</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እሳት፡ በሐቅለ፡ ሕሊና፡ ነዳዲ፡
                  ወበስመ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ መጥበቢተ፡ ዓለም፡ ዓባዲ፡
                  ማኅቶተ፡ ጸዳል፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ጽልመተ፡ አበሳ፡ ሰዳዲ፡
                  ከመ፡ እዜኑ፡ ኂሩተከ፡ ዕዳ፡ ኃጣውዕየ፡ ፍዲ፡
                  በአየረ፡ ሰማይ፡ ዘይጸርኅ፡ ቃልከ፡ ዓዋዲ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="13r" to="14v" facs="015">Fols 13r–14v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1325egziab">ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer nagśa
                                                  (General record)</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ብሂል፡
                  ንወድሶ፡ ለዘሀሎ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ልዑል፡
                  ስቡሕ፡ ወውዱስ፡ ዘሣረረ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዓለመ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ቃል፡
                  </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="14v" to="21v" facs="017">Fols 14v–21v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2915RepCh196">Malkǝʾ-hymn to
                                                  Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለፅንሰትከ፡ መሠረተ፡ ነገር፡ ወውጣኔ፡
                  ወለልደትከ፡ ሰላም፡ በብሥራተ፡ መልአክ፡ ሠናየ፡ ቅኔ፡
                  ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ ሰባኬ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ውስተ፡ ኵርጓኔ፡
                  ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በኪዳንከ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይርአይ፡ ኩነኔ፡
                  በእንተዝ፡ ኃሠሥኩ፡ ኪያከ፡ መድኃኔ፡
                  </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="22r" to="28v" facs="024">Fols 22r–28v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2927RepCh208">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ ቡሩክ፡
                  በበዓለ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ወመስቀለ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አምላክ፡
                  ገባሬ፡ መንክራት፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ በዓውደ፡ ዱድያኖስ፡ ምዑክ፡
                  አጽራርየ፡ እለ፡ ተንሥኡ፡ በነገረ፡ ከንቱ፡ ወበክ፡
                  ሐመደ፡ ለይኩን፡ በጽባሕ፡ ወሠርክ፡
                  </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="29r" to="44v" facs="031">Fols 29r–44v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="45r" to="53r" facs="047">Fols 45r–53r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2965RepCh246">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Gabrǝʾel</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
